		<title>How to install Jelly Bean on your Samsung Galaxy S</title>
		<link>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/how-to-install-jelly-bean-on-your-samsung-galaxy-s</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/how-to-install-jelly-bean-on-your-samsung-galaxy-s#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 08 Aug 2012 02:08:15 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Mobile]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Softwares]]></category>
