		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=615</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/a-sneak-peak-to-the-new-coldbuffer-blog"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/themes/evolve/library/media/images/blog-logo.png" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="ColdBuffer Blog" /></a>ColdBuffer Blog is currently undergoing a major update in terms of its overall look and feel. The new theme for the technology blog site features a clean and simple yet elegant design from Rocket Design which not only caters excellent user experience to some modern browsers, just as the current theme is, but to the old ones as well including the most hated browser by web developers &#8211; Internet Explorer 6. This is expected to bring the latest technology buzz[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter" title="ColdBuffer Blog" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/themes/evolve/library/media/images/blog-logo.png" alt="" width="200" height="90" /></p>
<p>ColdBuffer Blog is currently undergoing a major update in terms of its overall look and feel. The new theme for the technology blog site features a clean and simple yet elegant design from <a href="http://www.rocketdesign.be/" target="_blank">Rocket Design</a> which not only caters excellent user experience to some modern browsers, just as the current theme is, but to the old ones as well including the most hated browser by web developers &#8211; Internet Explorer 6. This is expected to bring the latest technology buzz to even more readers.</p>
<p>Many page elements of the current design are changed for better reading. Font size has been reduced tremendously to give more room to site contents such as media, articles, social plugins, etc. Awesome labels, overflowing across one side of the main container, are also added for  a cool change.</p>
<p>To give you an overview of how ColdBuffer Blog will appear in the coming days, you may view the gallery below. Click on the images to zoom</p>

<a href='http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/a-sneak-peak-to-the-new-coldbuffer-blog/coldbuffer-blog-contact'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/ColdBuffer-Blog-Contact-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="ColdBuffer Blog Contact" /></a>
<a href='http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/a-sneak-peak-to-the-new-coldbuffer-blog/coldbuffer-blog-comment'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/ColdBuffer-Blog-Comment-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="ColdBuffer Blog Comment" /></a>
<a href='http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/a-sneak-peak-to-the-new-coldbuffer-blog/coldbuffer-blog-index'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/ColdBuffer-Blog-Index-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="ColdBuffer Blog Index" /></a>

<p>The &#8220;evolution&#8221; happens very soon so stay tuned.</p>
