		<category><![CDATA[Pocari Sweat Dance Contest]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=596</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/pocari-sweat-dance-contest"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/pocari-sweat-dance-contest-300x281.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="pocari-sweat-dance-contest" /></a>Do you have a group whose members love dancing as much as you do? How about P100,000 in cold cash? If you do and the prize fascinates you, it&#8217;s time to wear those dancing shoes and groove with Pocari Sweat Dance Contest. Who can join: The contest is open to groups of five (5) to seven (7) whose members are: Filipinos residing in National Capital Region (NCR) 16 &#8211; 25 years of age How to join: To participate in the[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Pocari Sweat Dance Contest" href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/pocari-sweat-dance-contest.jpg" rel="lightbox"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-597" title="pocari-sweat-dance-contest" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/pocari-sweat-dance-contest-300x281.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="281" /></a></p>
<p>Do you have a group whose members love dancing as much as you do? How about P100,000 in cold cash? If you do and the prize fascinates you, it&#8217;s time to wear those dancing shoes and groove with Pocari Sweat Dance Contest.</p>
<p><strong>Who can join:</strong></p>
<p>The contest is open to groups of five (5) to seven (7) whose members are:</p>
<ul>
<li>Filipinos residing in National Capital Region (NCR)</li>
<li>16 &#8211; 25 years of age</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>How to join:</strong></p>
<p>To participate in the contest, interested groups are required to comply with the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>Like the <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pocarisweatphilippines" target="_blank">Pocari Sweat official fan page</a> either through the fan page itself or straight from the <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/pocaridancecontest" target="_blank">Pocari Sweat Dance Contest</a> Facebook application page.</li>
<li>Group representative must register the group details which include:
<ol type="a">
<li>Group Name</li>
<li>Name of Group Representative(*the first person in the list of group members)</li>
<li>Full name of group members</li>
<li>Address of all group members</li>
<li>Birthdates of all group members</li>
<li>Contact number of all group members</li>
<li>Valid e-mail address of all group members</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>Download the Pocari Sweat jingle and create a video of the group dancing to the tune of the jingle with the video showing the group drinking Pocari Sweat for at least 10 seconds.</li>
<li>Upload the video through the application page.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Judging of Entries:</strong></p>
<p>Entries will be judged according to the following criteria:</p>
<table width="100%" border="1" cellpadding="5">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope="col">Criteria</th>
<th scope="col">Percentage</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Choreography<br />
Refers to the Creativity, Incorporation of Pocari Sweat Drinking portion</td>
<td>30%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Over-All Impact<br />
Refers to the Participant&#8217;s Costume, Showmanship, Confidence, Freshness</td>
<td>20%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Number of Facebook Likes/Votes</span><br />
Refers to the total number of Facebook Fan Likes/Votes</td>
<td>30%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Expression</span><br />
Refers to Group interaction, Show of natural fun</td>
<td>20%</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>TOTAL</td>
<td>100%</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>Prizes at stake:</strong></p>
<table width="100%" border="0">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th scope="col" align="left" width="40%">One (1) Weekly Winner x 12 weeks</th>
<th scope="col" align="left" width="60%">Pocari Sweat Items worth Php1,500.00 + P10,000 cash (3 cases of Pocari Sweat 350mL; 72 bottles x P22 = Php1,584.00)</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><strong>Grand Prizes:</strong></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Grand Prize Winner</td>
<td>P100,000 cash</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>1st Runner-up Winner</td>
<td>P50,000 cash</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2nd Runner-up Winner</td>
<td>P30,000 cash</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p>Visit <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/pocaridancecontest" target="_blank">Pocari Sweat Dance Contest on Facebook</a> for more details.</p>
