		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=591</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/yahoo-messenger-11-is-now-available"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yahoo-messenger-11-150x150.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="yahoo-messenger-11" /></a>The Yahoo! Messenger team recently announced that Messenger 11 which was previously released in Beta is now on its release version and made available for download. The new version of the popular IM (instant message) client incorporates many bug fixes from the last stable release and enhanced the overall stability of the product. Yahoo! Messenger 11 also highlights new features for millions of its users worldwide. What&#8217;s new in Yahoo! Messenger 11? The latest version of Yahoo! Messenger contains a[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Yahoo! Messenger" href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yahoo-messenger-11.jpg" rel="lightbox"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-592" title="yahoo-messenger-11" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/yahoo-messenger-11.jpg" alt="" width="204" height="204" /></a></p>
<p>The Yahoo! Messenger team recently announced that Messenger 11 which was previously released in Beta is now on its release version and made available for download. The new version of the popular IM (instant message) client incorporates many bug fixes from the last stable release and enhanced the overall stability of the product. Yahoo! Messenger 11 also highlights new features for millions of its users worldwide.</p>
<p><strong>What&#8217;s new in Yahoo! Messenger 11?</strong></p>
<p>The latest version of Yahoo! Messenger contains a number of new features which let you:</p>
<ul>
<li>Share and update your status, post comments and keep up with your conversations across Facebook and Yahoo! within your Yahoo! Messenger client.</li>
<li>Invite friends and play games online friends including Mafia Wars and Fishville</li>
<li>Chat with your online Facebook friends right from your Messenger</li>
<li>Have easy access to your conversation history from any device</li>
<li>Make free PC-to-PC calls and PC-to-phone calls for as low as 1¢ a minute</li>
<li>Chat with high quality full-screen video.</li>
<li>Personalize your chatting experience with new Yahoo! Messenger skins.</li>
</ul>
<p>Download Yahoo! Messenger 11 <a href="http://messenger.yahoo.com" target="_blank">here</a></p>
