		<title>When it&#8217;s more than just smart, it&#8217;s genius</title>
		<link>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/when-its-more-than-just-smart-its-genius</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/when-its-more-than-just-smart-its-genius#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 12 Jun 2011 02:04:24 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Mobile]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Technology]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Android]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[LG Electronics]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[LG Optimus]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[LG Optimus 2X]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[LG Optimus Black]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=490</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/when-its-more-than-just-smart-its-genius"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/LG-Optimus-Black-2x-300x247.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="LG-Optimus-Black-2x" /></a>The new generation of mobile computing competition highlights smartphones from various consumer electronics companies and phone manufacturers. Smartphones that scale from phones with traditional keypad to QWERTY keyboard and devices with capacitive or resistive touchscreens or a combination of both. A number of devices categorized as smartphones are now out in the mobile world and are powered by various mobile operating systems enabling them to perform more advanced mobile computing tasks. But what is it that makes a regular smartphone[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a title="LG Optimus Black and LG Optimus 2x" rel="lightbox" href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/LG-Optimus-Black-2x.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-540" title="LG-Optimus-Black-2x" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/LG-Optimus-Black-2x-300x247.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="247" /></a></p>
<p>The new generation of mobile computing competition highlights smartphones from various consumer electronics companies and phone manufacturers. Smartphones that scale from phones with traditional keypad to QWERTY keyboard and devices with capacitive or resistive touchscreens or a combination of both. A number of devices categorized as smartphones are now out in the mobile world and are powered by various mobile operating systems enabling them to perform more advanced mobile computing tasks. But what is it that makes a regular smartphone stand out among the rest and be worthy to be tagged as a <em>genius</em> phone?</p>
<p><strong>Impressive Processor</strong></p>
<p>A smartphone with an lightning fast dual-core processor inside is genius because it enables faster mobile browsing and smooth multitasking experience like never before on a mobile device.</p>
<p><strong>Innovative Digital Data Transmission</strong></p>
<p>Making use of HDMI or High-Definition Multimedia Interface to transmit uncompressed digital data is commonly attributed to personal computers (PCs) or video game consoles. HDMI on a smartphone? That&#8217;s genius!</p>
<p><strong>Stunning Camera</strong></p>
<p>A camera that can replace a camcorder or a digicam in capturing high-quality photos and captivating videos in 1080p Full HD plus a non-VGA front camera for a clearer video conferencing or video chatting makes a smartphone genius as it pushes the boundaries of the feature of a regular camera on a smartphone.</p>
<p><strong>Seamless Wireless Connectivity</strong></p>
<p>Connecting to a wireless network through DLNA (Digital Living Network Alliance)  network connectivity and WiFi (Wireless Fidelity) Direct using a smartphone is a genius way of sharing data wirelessly over a network.</p>
<p><strong>Excellent Display</strong></p>
<p>A genius phone has the latest display technology on it using Nova Display that can battle it out with today&#8217;s existing mobile display innovations. <strong> </strong></p>
<p>On top of these genius features, a genius phone has one of the modern days&#8217; genius mobile operating system from Google &#8211; Android.</p>
<p>So what we&#8217;re getting at is for a smartphone to be genius, it should have first in the world features never seen on a smartphone before, contains enhancement of existing ground-breaking features and pioneers innovation for a superb user experience.</p>
<p>Where to find a genius phone? Search no more as LG Electronics introduces two of their latest mobile devices that are worthy to be tagged as genius phones as they posses what it takes to be genius &#8211; LG Optimus 2X and LG Optimus Black. Why settle to just a smart when you can have a genius. Optimus is more than just smart. It’s genius. Visit <a href="http://www.lgoptimus.ph/" target="_blank">lgoptimus.ph</a> for more information!</p>
<fb:like href=http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/when-its-more-than-just-smart-its-genius font=></fb:like>]]></content:encoded>
