<p>The campaign mechanics is simple. A Facebook user just need to like <a title="Resorts World Manila" href="http://www.facebook.com/rwmanila" target="_blank">Resort World Manila</a>&#8216;s official Facebook fan page and register their details to the <a title="Resorts World Manila Fantastic" href="http://apps.facebook.com/rwm-fan-tastic" target="_blank">Resort World Manila Fantastic</a> application page to qualify for the digital raffle. The electronic raffle will take place immediately once the specific fan count mark above is reached.</p>
