		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=402</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/experience-the-new-healthy-options-website"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Healthy-Options-300x232.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="Healthy Options" /></a>Healthy Options launches the new and improved version of their website. The natural products store chain&#8217;s new website offers a fresh new look and feel, improves existing site features and introduces new ones for their avid site viewers and members of their loyalty program. New Look The most obvious change that happened to the Healthy Options website from the previous version is the user interface. The new site now comes with a redesigned layout which provides a better user experience[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p style="text-align: center;"><a title="Healthy Options" rel="lightbox" href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Healthy-Options.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-405" title="Healthy Options" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Healthy-Options-300x232.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="232" /></a></p>
<p>Healthy Options launches the new and improved version of their website. The natural products store chain&#8217;s new website offers a fresh new look and feel, improves existing site features and introduces new ones for their avid site viewers and members of their loyalty program.</p>
<p><strong>New Look</strong></p>
<p>The most obvious change that happened to the Healthy Options website from the previous version is the user interface. The new site now comes with a redesigned layout which provides a better user experience and an improved menu bar for easy navigation across the site pages. <strong></strong></p>
<p><strong>Enhanced Site Features</strong></p>
<p>The existing features of the Healthy Options website were retained with improved functionality. Take a look at the new News Digest page and you&#8217;ll now be able to read the articles as if you are literally reading from a newspaper or magazine within the page. The new stores page uses an interactive map to show the store&#8217;s location plotted on a Philippine map.</p>
<p><strong>Loyalty Program Integration</strong></p>
<p>The biggest addition to the Healthy Options website is the member login and registration wherein existing Healthy Options card holders (Green, Gold and Titanium) will be able to check their current points online through the website. Members can also view their last transaction, check when their card is needed to be renewed, have discounts and so on. They can also update their details online without the need for them to physically go to a Healthy Options store.</p>
<p>Visit <a href="http://www.healthyoptions.com.ph">http://www.healthyoptions.com.ph</a> for more of the new changes made for Healthy Options.</p>
