		<title>Kit Kat Fastbreak Surprise</title>
		<link>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/kitkat-fastbreak-surprise</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/kitkat-fastbreak-surprise#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 13 May 2011 08:03:09 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Food]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Places and Events]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Break Out The Love]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[facebook application]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[KitKat Fastbreak Surprise]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[KitKat Philippines]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Nestle 100]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Nestle Philippines]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=321</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/kitkat-fastbreak-surprise"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Kitkat-150x150.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="Kit Kat" /></a>Nestle Kit Kat Philippines launches a new Facebook application today so as to introduce the brand&#8217;s new flavors now made available in the country &#8211; Kit Kat Orange, Kit Kat White, Kit Kat Dark and Kit Kat Mint. The popular chocolate brand from Nestle is giving away fabulous Apple gadgets for Kit Kat Fastbreak Surprise. The Mechanics: The promotion is open to all Filipino citizens preferably residing within Metro Manila. In order to be eligible for Kit Kat Fastbreak Surprise,[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Kitkat.jpg" rel="lightbox" title="Kit Kat"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-322" title="Kit Kat" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Kitkat-169x300.jpg" alt="" width="169" height="300" /></a></p>
<p>Nestle Kit Kat Philippines launches a new Facebook application today so as to introduce the brand&#8217;s new flavors now made available in the country &#8211; Kit Kat Orange, Kit Kat White, Kit Kat Dark and Kit Kat Mint. The popular chocolate brand from Nestle is giving away fabulous Apple gadgets for Kit Kat Fastbreak Surprise.</p>
<p><strong>The Mechanics:</strong><br />
The promotion is open to all Filipino citizens preferably residing within Metro Manila. In order to be eligible for Kit Kat Fastbreak Surprise, a Facebook user may first &#8220;like&#8221; the brand&#8217;s Facebook <a href="http://www.facebook.com/kitkat.ph" target="_blank">fan page</a> then register their details to the <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/kitkatfastbreak">application page</a>. The application automatically recognizes all Facebook users who joined previous Kit Kat campaign, <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/kitkatbreakthelove">Break Out The Love</a> and their details will be preloaded in the registration page. After successfully registering, the user must avail the &#8220;deal&#8221;.</p>
<p><strong>The Deals:</strong><br />
The application offers four deals, each of which covers 2 weeks and are further described as follows:</p>
<ul>
<li>May 13 – May 26 : Purchase one (1) Muti-pack KIT KAT Orange and get a chance to win an iPad 2</li>
<li>May 27 – June 9 : Purchase six (6) KIT KAT Dark packs and get a chance to win an MacBook Air</li>
<li>June 18 – July 1 : Purchase six (6) KIT KAT White packs and get a chance to win an iPhone 4</li>
<li>July 2 – July 15 : Purchase one (1) Multi-pack KIT KAT Mint and get a chance to win a iPad 2</li>
</ul>
<p>A participant can only avail for a particular deal once but may participate the other deals in the subsequent weeks. The prize for each deal will only be given away if the deal is &#8220;on&#8221; or once the number of registered users who availed for the deal reached 5000.</p>
<p><strong>Getting the Deal Prize:</strong><br />
If the deal is on at the end of deal duration, the application organizers will reveal a specific venue where to get the prize. The first participant to arrive at the location announced by the organizers at the time specified will be eligible to win the prize. The winner must present a valid ID and a proof of purchase indicated in the confirmation email he/she received.</p>
<p><strong>Consolation Prizes:</strong><br />
The next 20 validated participants with their valid proof of purchase and identification will also get Kit Kat gift packs while the 100th participant to arrive at the location will receive Centennial Gift and a KIT KAT Gift pack.</p>
<p>Visit <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/kitkatfastbreak" target="_blank">http://apps.facebook.com/kitkatfastbreak</a> now!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
