		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=270</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/vlc-1-1-9-is-now-available-for-download"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/largeVLC-150x150.png" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="largeVLC" /></a>VLC  media player,  a free and open source cross-platform multimedia player and framework that plays most multimedia files as well as DVD, Audio CD, VCD, and various streaming protocols, has its 1.1.9 version released. The new software upate fixes some important bugs and addresses security issues which includes the following: Security update regarding a heap-based buffer overflow in mp4 demuxer Update of libmodplug for security reasons in Windows and Mac versions Major updates in most language translations Numerous updates and[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/largeVLC.png" rel="lightbox" title="VLC Media Player"><img class="aligncenter size-thumbnail wp-image-271" title="largeVLC" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/largeVLC-150x150.png" alt="" width="150" height="150" /></a></p>
<p>VLC  media player,  a free and open source cross-platform multimedia player and                     framework that plays most multimedia files as well as DVD, Audio CD,                     VCD, and various streaming protocols, has its 1.1.9 version released. The new software upate fixes some important bugs and addresses security issues which includes the following:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.videolan.org/security/sa1103.html">Security update</a> regarding a heap-based buffer overflow in mp4 demuxer</li>
<li>Update of libmodplug for security reasons in Windows and Mac versions</li>
<li>Major updates in most language translations</li>
<li>Numerous updates and fixes on the interface and look of VLC for Mac OS X</li>
<li>Growl is bundled with VLC on Mac OS X now</li>
<li>Many miscellaneous fixes</li>
</ul>
<p>The intallation file of the new version takes up to 20MB and can be downloaded automatically by opening the media player, if you have it installed previously, or through their <a href="http://www.videolan.org/vlc/releases/1.1.9.html" target="_blank">website</a>.</p>
<p>VLC media player is created by VideoLAN Organization, s project and a non-profit organization, composed of volunteers developing and promoting free, open-source multimedia solutions.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
