		<category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[iOS]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[iOS 4.3]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=253</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/apple-releases-ios-4-3-3-software-update"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/hero20110302-150x150.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="hero20110302" /></a>Photo Credits: Apple.com The latest software update of Apple&#8217;s mobile operating system known as iOS is now available for free download weeks after the consumer electronics company released the 4.3.2 version (Click here to read the related post). The iOS 4.3.3 software update contains changes to the iOS crowd-sourced location database cache which includes the following: Reduces the size of the cache No longer backs the cache up to iTunes Deletes the cache entirely when Location Services is turned off[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/hero20110302.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-165" title="hero20110302" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/hero20110302-300x85.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="85" /></a><br />
<small>Photo Credits: Apple.com</small></p>
<p>The latest software update of Apple&#8217;s mobile operating system known as iOS is now available for free download weeks after the consumer electronics company released the 4.3.2 version (Click <a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=164">here</a> to read the related post). The iOS 4.3.3 software update contains changes to the iOS crowd-sourced location database cache which includes the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>Reduces the size of the cache</li>
<li>No longer backs the cache up to iTunes</li>
<li>Deletes the cache entirely when Location Services is turned off</li>
</ul>
<p>The following Apple mobile devices are made compatible for the free update:</p>
<ul>
<li>iPhone 4 (GSM model)</li>
<li>iPhone 3GS</li>
<li>iPad 2</li>
<li>iPad</li>
<li>iPod touch (4th generation)</li>
<li>iPod touch (3rd generation)</li>
</ul>
<p>iOS 4.3.3 software update takes about 650MB in file size.</p>
