		<title>MunchPunch</title>
		<link>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/munchpunch</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/munchpunch#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 03 May 2011 15:36:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Food]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Mobile]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[food]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[menus]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[MunchPunch]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Nokia]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Ovi Store]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[promos]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[restaurant]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[reviews]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=222</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/munchpunch"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/MunchPunch-150x150.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="MunchPunch" /></a>Looking for something to eat that would fit your budget? Or a restaurant near you? Or the latest dining promos? Or simply purchasing your next meal online? Here&#8217;s you&#8217;re perfect pick &#8211; MunchPunch. MunchPunch is the leading restaurant listing site in the Philippines holding records of thousands of different food establishments all over the country. From location, to restaurant menus and reviews, to the online promos and ordering online. Name it, MunchPunch has it all. Searching your next food trip[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/MunchPunch.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-223" title="MunchPunch" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/MunchPunch-300x179.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="179" /></a><br />
Looking for something to eat that would fit your budget? Or a restaurant near you? Or the latest dining promos? Or simply purchasing your next meal online? Here&#8217;s you&#8217;re perfect pick &#8211; <a href="http://www.munchpunch.com/">MunchPunch</a>.</p>
<p>MunchPunch is the leading restaurant listing site in the Philippines holding records of thousands of different food establishments all over the country. From location, to restaurant menus and reviews, to the online promos and ordering online. Name it, MunchPunch has it all. Searching your next food trip venue can be as easy as a, b, c thanks to MunchPunch&#8217;s intuitive search mechanism &#8211; by location, by mall, by cuisine and by tag.</p>
<p>MunchPunch doesn&#8217;t just simply list restaurant names and location. Try searching for a restaurant and you&#8217;ll be amazed &#8211; almost all relevant information about a specific restaurant will be given to you for FREE. Telephone numbers, website, business hours, estimated budget and even the payment methods accepted by the restaurant are displayed. It also indicates whether or not a restaurant has an online ordering which is a helpful tool for our busy employees.</p>
<p>If you want to share your experience dining in a restaurant, be it for customer service, food taste or the ambiance, you may drop your restaurant review for others to read. This requires logging in though so you need to create an account if you don&#8217;t have one. A process that takes only minutes &#8211; not a pain.</p>
<p>On the go and don&#8217;t have access to a laptop or desktop? Don&#8217;t worry MunchPunch is also available on your mobile. Simply logon to http://m.munchpunch.com and enjoy all the great features from the web version. Too lazy to type in URLs on your mobile? You may dowload the Ovi app version on your compatible Nokia device. Just search for &#8220;MunchPunch&#8221; on the Ovi Store to download and install.</p>

<a href='http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/munchpunch/scr000035'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/Scr000035-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Scr000035" /></a>
