<p>Do you want a cool smartphone this summer? Squeeze your brain cells and solve the Nokia E7 Puzzle game to get a chance to take home the brand new Nokia E7. Put the puzzle pieces together, as you normally do on a regular jigsaw puzzle, as fast as you can. The Nokia fan with the least time spent solving the puzzle all throughout the promo duration wins.</p>
<p><strong>Mechanics</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Like the Nokia Facebook fan page<strong> </strong></li>
<li>Allow the application to access your profile information, post to your wall, etc.</li>
<li>Register your details</li>
<li>Play the game as fast as you can</li>
</ul>
<p>Visit the <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/esevenpuzzle" target="_blank">application</a> to view the complete <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/esevenpuzzle" target="_blank">promo mechanics</a>.  <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/esevenpuzzle" target="_blank">Terms and conditions</a> apply.</p>
<p>Promo runs from April 21, 2011 until May 19, 2011 and the winner, who will win a brand new Nokia E7, will be announced on the 3rd week of May, 2011 on the <a href="http://www.facebook.com/nokiaphilippines" target="_blank">Nokia Philippines</a> Facebook fan page.</p>
