		<category><![CDATA[Villa Cayabyab Resort]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=151</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/enhs-batch-2003-reunion"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/208273_1914543950832_1458948464_2131054_5484885_n-150x150.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="208273_1914543950832_1458948464_2131054_5484885_n" /></a>Photo credits: Julie Ann Lumiguen Seeing friends and batchmates again after 8 years refreshes the old times yet memorable experiences with them over the years. Getting together again means a lot of things &#8211; reminiscing the moments you&#8217;ve shared in the past, updating your friends with what you have accomplished so far in the present, and sharing what you plan to do in the future to name a few. Preparations Several months before April 2011, our friends from our beloved[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/208273_1914543950832_1458948464_2131054_5484885_n.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-153" title="208273_1914543950832_1458948464_2131054_5484885_n" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/208273_1914543950832_1458948464_2131054_5484885_n-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="225" /></a><br />
<small>Photo credits: Julie Ann Lumiguen</small></p>
<p>Seeing friends and batchmates again after 8 years refreshes the old times yet memorable experiences with them over the years. Getting together again means a lot of things &#8211; reminiscing the moments you&#8217;ve shared in the past, updating your friends with what you have accomplished so far in the present, and sharing what you plan to do in the future to name a few.</p>
<p><strong>Preparations</strong></p>
<p>Several months before April 2011, our friends from our beloved Alma Mater, Estanza National High School, posted the announcement over the net through the well-known social networking site. A number of discussions and suggestions were raised including the date and the venue where the reunion will be held. The administrators even came up with an online poll to know everyone&#8217;s choice as to the venue of the upcoming event.</p>
<p><strong>The Reunion</strong></p>
<p>After months of careful preparations, the much-awaited ENHS Batch 2003&#8242;s first ever get together party finally took place on April 16 &#8211; 17, 2011 in Villa Cayabyab Resort, Malimpuec, Lingayen, Pangasinan. Swimming, videoke, <em>lamon</em> with alcolohic drinks on the side, <em>kulitan </em>sessions are some of the activities. The group spent whole day and whole night in the resort though some needs to go so soon because of work-related stuff.</p>
<p><strong>Thank You&#8217;s</strong></p>
<p>Thanks and congratulations to the organizers of the event for the successful reunion of our high school batch. Also, thank you to those who have shared their precious times with us in this event. Thanks to the following (in no particular order and hope this is complete hehe):</p>
<ul>
<li>Julie Pearl Soriano</li>
<li>Glaiza Ballesteros</li>
<li>Paz Cheri Ann Valencerina</li>
<li>Julie Ann Lumiguen</li>
<li>Jhaymarie Estrada</li>
<li>Katrina Villanueva</li>
<li>Richi-lyn Silva</li>
<li>Leny Enierga</li>
<li>Ellen Sheira Castro</li>
<li>Catherine Victorio</li>
<li>Marilyn Parangat</li>
<li>Jayson Estrada</li>
<li>Jayson Garcia</li>
<li>Jayson Soriano</li>
<li>Michael Mangapot</li>
<li>Ardie dela Cruz</li>
<li>Al Cris Domingo</li>
<li>Mark Macagba</li>
<li>May Valenzuela</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Remembrance</strong><br />
<a href="http://www.facebook.com/media/set/fbx/?set=a.1914543550822.110086.1458948464" target="_blank"><br />
1st get2gether ENHS batch&#8217;03!..4.16.11 part1<br />
</a> by Julie Ann Lumiguen<br />
<a href="http://www.facebook.com/media/set/fbx/?set=a.1710124117268.2085293.1363058191" target="_blank"><br />
