		<title>Send E-cards To Your Mom This Mother&#8217;s Day!</title>
		<link>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/send-your-moms-e-cards-this-mothers-day</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/send-your-moms-e-cards-this-mothers-day#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Tue, 12 Apr 2011 00:05:23 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Places and Events]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Web]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[EDSA Billboard]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[facebook]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[facebook application]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[iframe application]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Mother's Day]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[NIDO Say It Big]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=48</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/send-your-moms-e-cards-this-mothers-day"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/NidoSayItBig-150x150.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="NidoSayItBig" /></a>Thinking of a gift for your mom this mother&#8217;s day on a tight budget? Don&#8217;t worry Nestlé will take care of that. How? NIDO FORTIFIED® just launched a Facebook Application which lets children of all ages send electronic cards (e-cards) to their moms with their photos on them- NIDO FORTIFIED® SAY IT BIG. Isn&#8217;t that cool? No more expensive gift buys or anything. All you need to have is a Facebook account, who doesn&#8217;t have anyway? It only takes minutes[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Thinking of a gift for your mom this mother&#8217;s day on a tight budget? Don&#8217;t worry Nestlé will take care of that. How? NIDO FORTIFIED® just launched a Facebook Application which lets children of all ages send electronic cards (e-cards) to their moms with their photos on them- NIDO FORTIFIED® SAY IT BIG. Isn&#8217;t that cool? No more expensive gift buys or anything. All you need to have is a Facebook account, who doesn&#8217;t have anyway? It only takes minutes to create this so it won&#8217;t hurt if you&#8217;re doing it in an internet shop.</p>
<p><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/NidoSayItBig.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-98" title="NidoSayItBig" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/NidoSayItBig-300x298.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="298" /></a></p>
<p>Just log on to your Facebook account and click <a href="http://apps.facebook.com/say-it-big">here</a> to go the application page. Liking the NIDO FORTIFIED® fan page and letting the application know your details are the only things you need to start creating your e-card. Make sure you read the application&#8217;s terms and conditions, photo and message guidelines to increase your entry&#8217;s chances of being approved. Approval of entries takes around 24 hours.</p>
<p>Once approved, you and your mom will be notified via email containing a link where you can have the e-card previewed. If enabled, the application will also automatically update your Facebook status to let your friends know that your card has been approved and for them to do the same as well. Awesome! Not only that. There&#8217;s more? Yeah, there&#8217;s more. Each approved e-cards gets to be displayed on the large electronic billboards in EDSA namely SM North EDSA and EDSA Boni. How does that sound? Just check your email confirmation to know when will your e-card be shown for that extra special gift for your mom this mother&#8217;s day.</p>
<p>Here&#8217;s a sample of what you will expect if your entry has been approved by the application administrators. What do you say? Isn&#8217;t it awesome?</p>
<p><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/IMG_7280.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-100" title="NIDO Say It Big Entry" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/IMG_7280-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></a></p>
<p>The application runs from April 12 &#8211; May 31, 2011.</p>
<p>What are you waiting for? Have your photo with your mom taken now and create your electronic card to express how special she is. Remember you don&#8217;t have to say it loud. All you have to do is SAY IT BIG! Good luck!</p>
<fb:like href=http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/send-your-moms-e-cards-this-mothers-day font=></fb:like>]]></content:encoded>
