		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/79"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/lg-optimus-3d-p920-1-1-150x150.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="lg-optimus-3d-p920-1 (1)" /></a>LG Electronics announced its very first 3D smartphone &#8211; LG Optimus 3D P920. Equipped with Dual-core 1GHz ARM Cortex-A9 proccessor, dual-memory with PowerVR SGX540 GPU and TI OMAP4430 chipset and works on quad band GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 with tri band HSDPA 900/ 1800/ 1900 network, this phone will surely catch every techy guys&#8217; attention and will definitely change the way we communicate. LG Optimus 3D lets you capture and preview/playback 3D images and videos, thanks to its[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/lg-optimus-3d-p920-1-1.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-80" title="lg-optimus-3d-p920-1 (1)" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/lg-optimus-3d-p920-1-1.jpg" alt="" width="383" height="357" /></a></p>
<p>LG Electronics announced its very first 3D smartphone &#8211; LG Optimus 3D P920. Equipped with Dual-core 1GHz ARM Cortex-A9 proccessor, dual-memory with PowerVR SGX540 GPU and TI OMAP4430 chipset and works on quad band GSM 850 / 900 / 1800 / 1900 with tri band HSDPA 900/ 1800/ 1900 network, this phone will surely catch every techy guys&#8217; attention and will definitely change the way we communicate. LG Optimus 3D lets you capture and preview/playback 3D images and videos, thanks to its dedicated dual 5MP autofocus cameras with LED flash and geo-tagging support.</p>
<p>For full phone specifications, please refer to table below.</p>
