		<title>Nokia E72 Firmware Update</title>
		<link>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/nokia-e72-firmware-update</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/nokia-e72-firmware-update#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 09 Apr 2011 18:43:04 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Technology]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[54.005]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Firmware Update]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Nokia]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Symbian OS]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=38</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/nokia-e72-firmware-update"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Nokia-E72-620x457.jpg" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="Nokia-E72-620x457" /></a>A new firmware update (ver. 54.005) for Nokia E72 is now available for download. The update includes a minor bug fix from update of the previous version, general usability and performance improvements. To install the update on your device, try the following options: Over the air: From standby mode, dial *#0000#. Select Options &#62; Check for updates. Choose Software Updates from Nokia Ovi Suite. &#160; &#160;]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>A new firmware update (ver. 54.005) for Nokia E72 is now available for download. The update includes a minor bug fix from update of the previous version, general usability and performance improvements.</p>
<p>To install the update on your device, try the following options:</p>
<p>Over the air: From standby mode, dial *#0000#. Select Options &gt; Check for updates.</p>
<p>Choose Software Updates from Nokia Ovi Suite.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Nokia-E72-620x457.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-39" title="Nokia-E72-620x457" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/Nokia-E72-620x457.jpg" alt="" width="496" height="366" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<fb:like href=http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/nokia-e72-firmware-update font=></fb:like>]]></content:encoded>
