		<title>Sombrero Island</title>
		<link>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/sombrero-island</link>
		<comments>http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/sombrero-island#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sat, 09 Apr 2011 18:15:06 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Places and Events]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Anilao]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Batangas]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Sombrero Island]]></category>

		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/?p=16</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[<a href="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/sombrero-island"><img align="left" hspace="5" width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/plugins/thumbnail-for-excerpts/tfe_no_thumb.png" class="alignleft wp-post-image tfe" alt="" title="" /></a>Looking for a perfect escapade this summer? Well, you might want to consider this fantastic island in Anilao Batangas &#8211; Sombrero Island. Location: North of Sepok Point, the northern end of Maricaban Island. Access: 12-15 min by boat from EAGLE POINT pier Southwest across the Maricaban Strait until Northwest of Sombrero Island. Conditions for diving: Generally calm with a strong current, but it can get rough on the surface. Visibility can reach up to 25m (80ft) Average depth: 10m (33ft)[...]]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Looking for a perfect escapade this summer? Well, you might want to consider this fantastic island in Anilao Batangas &#8211; Sombrero Island.</p>
<p><strong>Location:</strong><br />
North of Sepok Point, the northern end of Maricaban Island.</p>
<p><strong>Access:</strong><br />
12-15 min by boat from EAGLE POINT pier Southwest across the Maricaban Strait until Northwest of Sombrero Island.</p>
<p><strong>Conditions for diving:</strong><br />
Generally calm with a strong current, but it can get rough on the surface. Visibility can reach up to 25m (80ft)</p>
<p><strong>Average depth:</strong><br />
10m (33ft)</p>
<p><strong>Maximum depth:</strong><br />
18m (60ft)</p>

<a href='http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/sombrero-island/attachment/09042010043'><img width="150" height="150" src="http://blogs.coldbuffer.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/09042010043-150x150.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="09042010043" /></a>
